name: Normal Clopsi egg
description:
This is a Clopsi egg. Its owner has little chance to receive baby Clopsi from us randomly and free of charge. 

The more the number of the eggs you own, the more is your chance to win the baby.

The value of a Clopsi egg is very low, but in comparison, the price of  a baby is several ten folds more.
Some of the mother lacking eggs will be expired gradually.

/////// For further information follow us  on the social media. ///////

The story of mother Clopsi: Mother Clopsi, who was one of the unknown Semi-Goddesses,  becomes severely injured in the great war and gets herself into a shelter. She leaves this world, burns like Phoenix and changes into cinders. Among her remainder cinders 10,000 Clopsi eggs were found.
